summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Keystone Place, from North Fiftieth Street to North Fifty-fifth Street et al, in the City of Seattle, by grading under Ordinance No. 18656, creating Local Improvement District No. 1757 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
